{"tid":2337804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"展抗中決心？拜登團隊施壓歐盟，對中國投資協議踩煞車","createTime":"2020-12-23T14:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T18:10:17.000Z","uid":78519,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9b73b7be8eced5cb0ab9e4195f22c0d7db783547","tid":2337804,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:23:39.000Z","msg":"即將上任的拜登團隊展現出抗中決心，施壓歐盟放慢腳步，不要急於在今年底前和中國簽訂投資協議。<br />\n<br />\n拜登政府的新任國安顧問蘇利文（Jake Sullivan）Twitter 稱，拜登、賀錦麗當局歡迎歐洲夥伴，提早就雙方共同憂慮的中國經濟作法展開磋商。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jakejsullivan/status/1341180109118726144?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjakejsullivan%2Fstatus%2F1341180109118726144%3Fs%3D21&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp2WzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=146a02ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjakejsullivan%2Fstatus%2F1341180109118726144%3Fs%3D21&h=45ed4c28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jakejsullivan/status/1341180109118726144?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博社報導，歐盟和中國急於在今年底前，簽訂全面性投資協定（Comprehensive Agreement on Investment），以便打開中國市場、消除歧視性作法。但是批評者說，北京鐵腕鎮壓香港和新疆的異議份子，簽署合約有如獎勵北京、給予他們歐洲市場的優惠准入。墨卡托中國研究所（Mercator Institute for China Studies）主管 Mikko Huotari 說，協議是中國的「象徵性勝利」，會讓歐美更難組成聯合陣線對抗中國。<br />\n<br />\n金融時報報導，據了解拜登當局關注歐中投資協定，是擔憂歐洲在中國強迫勞動議題上，態度不夠強硬。觀察家呼籲，歐盟應該暫緩和中國談判，等到拜登就任後再做打算。<br />\n<br />\n蘇利文獲國安顧問提名後，只在 Twitter 推過 10 條推文，其中 3 則針對中國。蘇利文先前推文指控，中國逮捕民主人士，等於攻擊香港民眾的自由。他寫到：「我們與盟友和夥伴站在一起，共抗中國對香港自由的襲擊──並要協助受迫害者找到避難所」。<br />\n<br />\n今年稍早，拜登曾說中國國家主席習近平是「惡棍」（thug），身上沒半根民主骨頭。拜登表示，川普主政下，美國和歐亞盟友的關係受創，他的當務之急是重建聯盟關係。此外，蘇利文和美國下任國務卿布林肯（Antony Blinken）也強調美國和歐洲應該更密切合作，應對中國挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/12/23/biden-pressured-the-eu-to-unite-against-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F12%2F23%2Fbiden-pressured-the-eu-to-unite-against-china%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp2WzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=efe95498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/12/23/biden-pressured-the-eu-to-unite-against-china/</a>"},{"pid":"d37e35b7ccc4e2591addf6adc4c9491c681a1cf8","tid":2337804,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"煞停!<br />\n美國又要join <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a08332c3e549c08d5789dfa2e2078bb097b031","tid":2337804,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:30:23.000Z","msg":"joe食埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efee04201bd6db58bbf4ef72accfce57b8a9f79b","tid":2337804,"uid":88399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"9UP唔洗成本<br />\n望下自己D內閭成員先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3919eac1654e0556fec41e98d518127ab9424b8e","tid":2337804,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"歐洲投降協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c54d8860161ae369fb5e5b3b5617a673ab73f74","tid":2337804,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:05:48.000Z","msg":"JOE: 今年未送幻幻"},{"pid":"ab63dc57a50f39b601469f040643f46112af0a7f","tid":2337804,"uid":70771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:07:27.000Z","msg":"口交下當交戲，之後兩頭擺都攞個交代咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc304cd518a82a560bc7cdd7234ea697e1c377b1","tid":2337804,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"要等埋登叔嘛<br />\n唔係點同主人講佢成功爭取"},{"pid":"8a6cc471df38cc842dc1ea46b8a96c69fc6faf8e","tid":2337804,"uid":324629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ab63dc57a50f39b601469f040643f46112af0a7f","tid":2337804,"uid